snippet.title: Missile Conflict BLITZ  - The arcade classic Missile Command reinvented - Official Release Trailer
snippet.description:
This is the official Missile Conflict BLITZ Trailer.

Missile Conflict BLITZ is a homage and reinvention to the great arcade classic Missile Command. Download this android and iOS mobile game from GooglePlay and the iOS App Store.

Get it here
https://rooncave.com/get-missile-conflict-blitz
